specified in Table 2 were taken into consideration for service, berthing maneuvers, and unberthing maneuver processes. The StatFit program included in ProModel simulation software was used to identify suitable distributions for these processes. Kolmogorov-Smirnov (K-S) and Anderson-Darling (A-D) goodness of fit tests were conducted.
Findings
The statistical analysis findings of the ship operation processes were examined under the titles of “Ship Arrival”, “Service”, “Berthing Maneuver and Unberthing Maneuver”.

